sourceMeaningMnemonic: The only <radical>woman</radical> in this <radical>city</radical> is your <kanji>older sister</kanji>. She's the only woman surrounded by a bunch of men, but she's following her dreams in the big city.
meaningInfo: You want to go to the city someday, but you're not old enough yet, like your older sister is.
readingMnemonic: Your <kanji>older sister</kanji> may have moved to the city, but she kept her pet <reading>shee</reading>p (<ja>し</ja>) with her. Now the only woman in the city is your older sister, and the only sheep is her pet.
readingInfo: Picture your older sister and her sheep walking through the city. Everyone turns to stare at them, because they're the only ones of their kind.
